name: Prebel
title: Guild Master
notes: Guild Master. Author of the 6 Dens Principles for boundary mapping.

name: Kerith Moll
title: Guild Master Assessor
notes: Assessed Vornis Keth's predictive cartography work.

name: Tomas Grell

notes: Elder cartographer. Trained Vagabu. Foundational Dens border mapping.

title: Cartographer
notes: Daughter of Tomas. Specialized in Yeller Quarry route mapping.

name: Vagabu Olt
title: Wandering Sketcher
notes: Not a formal member. Associate status. Travels in pickbox cart.

name: Gareth Poll
title: Cartographer
notes: Modern cartographer. Extended Bagbu's work.

name: Captain Vrell
title: Military Liaison
notes: Military officer with Guild liaison role.

notes: Founder of systematic exploration program.

name: Vass Tonner

notes: Opposes Drusk's standardization efforts.

name: Jara Torval
title: Associate Surveyor
notes: Also a taxonomist. Sister of Wen Torval.

name: Foreman Hask
title: Trade Route Master
notes: Led Merchant Guild trade route survey.

name: Administrator Venn
title: Census Administrator
notes: Handles census and population surveys.

name: Rella Tarn
title: Expedition Leader
notes: Led the disastrous Ninth Expedition.

name: Lurra Venn
title: Pattern Analyst
notes: Proposed trader archetype classification system.

name: Meck Drune

name: Swick
title: Bootleg Archivist
notes: Backroom book collector. Makes maps. Operates outside official channels.

name: Old Murch
title: Elder Advisor
notes: Murchison Toller. Philosopher. Twenty-Ten member.

name: Prebel Cord
title: Reconstructionist

name: Pollux Dann
